---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="building">
  <main class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4 sm:p-8">
    <div class="max-w-2xl font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm text-white uppercase space-y-4 sm:space-y-8">
      <div class="relative border border-white/60 px-4 py-2 inline-block">
        <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/60">┌</span>
        <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/60">┐</span>
        <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/60">└</span>
        <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/60">┘</span>
        <span class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold">Building</span>
      </div>
      <div class="relative border border-white/30 px-4 py-2 text-white/60 text-xs block w-fit">
        <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┌</span>
        <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┐</span>
        <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">└</span>
        <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┘</span>
        I like building AI-native tools, open-source projects, and things that make me curious.
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-8">
        <div class="relative border border-white/30 px-3 py-3 sm:px-5 sm:py-4 space-y-2">
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┌</span>
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┐</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">└</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┘</span>
          <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">2026</div>
          <a href="https://graphene-nu.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-bold underline hover:text-white/70 block">Graphene</a>
          <div class="text-white/70 text-xs">Open source research paper management with AI.</div>
          <div class="text-white/60 text-xs"><a href="https://github.com/lance116/Graphene" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white">github</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative border border-white/30 px-3 py-3 sm:px-5 sm:py-4 space-y-2">
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┌</span>
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┐</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">└</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┘</span>
          <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">2024</div>
          <a href="https://correkt.ai/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-bold underline hover:text-white/70 block">Correkt</a>
          <div class="text-white/70 text-xs">World's first multimodal search engine. 40k+ users.</div>
          <div class="text-white/60 text-xs"><a href="https://github.com/Correkt" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white">github</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative border border-white/30 px-3 py-3 sm:px-5 sm:py-4 space-y-2">
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┌</span>
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┐</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">└</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┘</span>
          <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">2024</div>
          <div class="font-bold">Alexandria</div>
          <div class="text-white/70 text-xs">SDK and browser API for AI-powered in-page research.</div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 text-white/60 text-xs"><a href="https://github.com/zixihong/alexandria-research-api" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white">github</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative border border-white/30 px-3 py-3 sm:px-5 sm:py-4 space-y-2">
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┌</span>
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┐</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">└</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┘</span>
          <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">2024</div>
          <div class="font-bold">SnDBot</div>
          <div class="text-white/70 text-xs">AI-powered Speech and Debate Coach.</div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 text-white/60 text-xs"><a href="https://github.com/zixihong/sndbot" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white">github</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative border border-white/30 px-3 py-3 sm:px-5 sm:py-4 space-y-2">
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┌</span>
          <span class="absolute -top-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┐</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -left-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">└</span>
          <span class="absolute -bottom-[0.7em] -right-[0.5em] bg-black px-[3px] leading-none text-sm text-white/40">┘</span>
          <div class="text-white/60 text-xs">2024</div>
          <div class="font-bold">Bayes NBA</div>
          <div class="text-white/70 text-xs">Bayesian analysis of how an NBA player impacts teammates' shooting.</div>
          <div class="text-white/60 text-xs"><a href="https://github.com/zixihong/bayes-nba" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline hover:text-white">github</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-4">
        <a href="/" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white text-xs underline">← back</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
